---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Case studies
description: Real engagements, real outcomes.
permalink: /case-studies/
---

<div class="container">
  <h1>Case studies</h1>
  <p class="muted">How specific engagements played out — what we built, what changed.</p>

  {% if collections["case-studies"].length > 0 %}
    <ul class="post-list">
      {% for post in collections["case-studies"] %}
        <li>
          <a href="{{ post.url }}">
            <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
            <p class="muted small">
              {{ post.data.client }} · {{ post.data.industry }}{% if post.data.outcome_headline %} · {{ post.data.outcome_headline }}{% endif %}
            </p>
            {% if post.data.summary %}<p>{{ post.data.summary }}</p>{% endif %}
          </a>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  {% else %}
    <p class="muted">No case studies published yet.</p>
  {% endif %}
</div>
